Package ie.gmit.sw.language_distribution

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LangDistStore
    Represents a store of language distributions (LangDist objects) which are accessible through a set of Lang keys.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HashedLangDist
    Hashed language distribution; a language distribution where each k-mer is hashed into an array (there WILL be collisions, but since other language distributions of the same language would have the same collisions and so record frequencies for the same index, it should still work OK and be much more efficient than using Maps).
    LangDist
    Abstract definition for a language distribution, involving recording k-mer occurrences from language samples and creating a frequency distribution array.
    LangDistMap
    Represents a store of language distribution objects using a Map.
    LangDistStoreBuilder
    Builder pattern used to build language distribution stores.
